library-deqm.name: profile-library-deqm
library-deqm.description: The DEQM Library Profile describes a shareable, published library resource that can be used to share clinical knowledge

measure-deqm.name: profile-measure-deqm
measure-deqm.description: The DEQM Measure Profile describes a shareable, published measure resource that can be used to define an electronic clinical quality measure

measurereport-deqm.name: profile-measurereport-deqm
measurereport-deqm.description: The DEQM MeasureReport Profile represents the quality measure results that  the practitioner's organization convey to the payer.  It contains the references to other profiles  needed to attest to the measure.

extension-measureSubscription.name: The extension modifies the `criteria`  definiton to be a Measure instance id.
extension-measureSubscription.description: The extension modifies the `criteria`  definiton to be a Measure instance id.

subscription-deqm.name: profile-subscription-deqm
subscription-deqm.description: The DEQM Subscription Profile is defined for sending notifications to a subscriber (Aggregator) when a Provider system has determined the DEQM Measure data is ready as is  described in the  exchange of quality measure data [option 3](guidance.html#option-3-subscription-service-combined-with-the--collect-data-operation).
